Verdc., Kew Bull. 37: 462. 1982. (
<bibRefCitation id="D62FB48C922541E8DB03A34B927B180F" author="Verdcourt, B" journalOrPublisher="Kew Bulletin" pageId="213" pageNumber="214" pagination="459 - 464" publicationUrl="10.2307/4110047" refId="B375" refString="Verdcourt, B, 1982. Corrections and additions to the &quot;Flora of Tropical East Africa: Convolvulaceae &quot; V. Kew Bulletin 37: 459 - 464, DOI: 10.2307/4110047" title="Corrections and additions to the &quot; Flora of Tropical East Africa: Convolvulaceae &quot; V." url="10.2307/4110047" volume="37" year="1982">Verdcourt 1982</bibRefCitation>
